title: Balance Health Centers | Age Management Clinic Palm Beach Gardens FL
description: Balance Health Centers in Palm Beach Gardens, FL is dedicated to multi-disciplinary approach to integrative age management. For appointments, call  (561) 250-8422.
cleaned_text: Balance Health Centers in Tequesta, FL is dedicated to integrative age management, a healing-oriented approach that takes into account the whole person, including all aspects of one's lifestyle. Our team of medical providers employs a multi-disciplinary approach to age management medicine and is comprised of a board-certified and licensed physician, dietitian, and health care and wellness professionals dedicated to optimizing the quality of life.
